{
  "stem": "719.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I-- I don't think it's safe for you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he gave me the certificate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I would stand for hours in the line for my father and my mother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was so proud when I could come home with some rations, some food, some tea, sometimes dry goods to cook, you know, something like a-- a noodles-- something that a ration was allowed.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They used to say we're gonna have butter today.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody was standing for hours.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'll never forget how hard it was to be in the line with all these people, and standing there and waiting to be helped.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they came over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They screamed at me sometimes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What are you doing here-- in German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I would say, my father is sick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I was afraid to say sick, because then they started to get rid of sick people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so you-- you didn't know what to do; and the scares, the fear-- continuously, continuously living in that fear.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was from the beginning of '40, '41.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But in the midst of everything, I still had a group of Jewish girls-- what I'm trying to remember.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we met in a home illegally-- because that was very dangerous-- as a group of Zionist movement, to give us hope, to do something, to learn Hebrew songs, to get together-- risking, literally, our life.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was afraid to tell my parents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember one day, I came home, and my mother was so worried.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why are you going?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, I'm not going far.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We're not talking about miles away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was down the street, maybe, somewhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I met some people, and I learned about a socialist Zionist organization.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
